about.summary: This package computes the degrees of freedom of the lasso, elastic net, generalized elastic net and adaptive lasso based on the generalized path seeking algorithm.  The optimal model can be selected by model selection criteria including Mallows' Cp, bias-corrected AIC (AICc), generalized cross validation (GCV) and BIC.

name: r-msgps
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.3.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-msgps
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/msgps_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/msgps/msgps_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ffdaae8e64045556dcf698e19650296e2ec7e4751ab5b81009598a40b8061165

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 3
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('fortran') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_fortran') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('msgps')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('msgps')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://www.keihirose.com/.
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: This package computes the degrees of freedom of the lasso, elastic net, generalized
    elastic net and adaptive lasso based on the generalized path seeking algorithm.  The
    optimal model can be selected by model selection criteria including Mallows' Cp,
    bias-corrected AIC (AICc), generalized cross validation (GCV) and BIC.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
